description: ADATA steps up again with the launch of its S102 series USB 3.0 flash drives. This series is the industry's first to incorporate native controller chip for flash products, demonstrating once again the company's leadership role in the market. As ADATA brings the latest and fastest devices to the market. Our customers get to stand on the shoulders of a technological giant. So be one of the first to use this generations superior technology.
title: ADATA S102 16 GB USB 3.0 Flash Drive AS102-16G-RGY (Titanium Grey)
